channel.title: Nexus 718 run.bat error
channel.description:
Hello guys, i'm trying to use Nexus 718 source but i get this error when i'm trying to run the source.[code][Nexus] Server is loading.. [Launcher] Initing Cache... Exception in thread "main" java.lang.ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException: 19 at com.rs.utils.Utils.getItemDefinitionsSize(Utils.java:268) at com.rs.cache.loaders.ItemsEquipIds.init(ItemsEquipIds.java:13) at com.rs.Launcher.main(Launcher.java:63) Press any key to continue . . .
[/code]
